I = (I + CBC^T)(I + CBC^T)^{-1}.
I - C(C^TC + B^{-1})^{-1} C^T = I - (C^{-T} (C^TC) C^{-1} + C^{-T} B^{-1} C^{-1})^{-1} = I - (I + (CBC^T)^{-1})^{-1}.
(I + CBC^T)(I + (CBC^T)^{-1})^{-1} \stackrel{?}{=} CBC^T.
(CBC^T)^{-1}(CBC^T) = I
